| freight_amount | Confidential | Financial transaction value; unauthorized disclosure could reveal pricing strategies and commercial terms | Finance & Accounting | Financial Data |
| insurance_amount | Confidential | Financial insurance value; unauthorized disclosure could reveal cargo value and commercial terms | Finance & Accounting | Financial Data |
