INSERT INTO messages (id, conversation_id, role, content, created_at) VALUES (107, 39, 'assistant', 'I don''t see any uploaded data or file attached to your message. To generate comprehensive data quality rules across all four layers, I''ll need you to provide your data fields.

You can share your data in any of these formats:

**Option 1 — Field List**
Simply paste a list of field names:
```
customer_id, full_name, email, phone_number, vat_number, invoice_date, total_amount
```

**Option 2 — Table Structure**
Paste field names with data types:
```
customer_id       VARCHAR(50)
full_name         VARCHAR(200)
email             VARCHAR(100)
invoice_date      DATE
total_amount      DECIMAL(18,2)
```

**Option 3 — Sample Data**
Paste a few rows of actual data (headers + rows), and I''ll infer the field types and context automatically.

**Option 4 — Upload a File**
Upload your Excel (.xlsx), CSV, or any structured file directly in the chat.

---

Once you share the fields, I''ll generate a **full 4-layer DQ analysis** including:
- ✅ **Layer 1** — Technical rules (nulls, types, formats, lengths)
- ✅ **Layer 2** — Logical rules (ranges, date ordering, uniqueness)
- ✅ **Layer 3** — Business & cross-field rules (ZATCA/VAT compliance, conditionals, status logic)
- ✅ **Layer 4** — Business logic warnings (ambiguities, missing constraints, risky patterns)

Please go ahead and share your data! 🚀', '2026-03-04 11:03:48.205418');
