INSERT INTO messages (id, conversation_id, role, content, created_at) VALUES (148, 50, 'assistant', 'Here are the data classification results for the fields in the **shipment** sheet, based on the Saudi SDAIA NDMO data classification framework:

| Field Name | Classification Level | Classification Rationale | Data Owner | Sensitivity Category |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| shipment_id | Restricted | Internal system identifier used for record linkage. Disclosure outside the organization could enable unauthorized tracking of shipment volumes and patterns. | Customs & Logistics Data Owner | Internal Reference |
