          "rule_description": "container_no must follow ISO 6346 format: 4-letter owner code + 6-digit serial + 1 check digit (e.g., ''MAEU1234567''). Saudi Customs FASAH rejects non-standard container numbers.",
          "rule_expression": "IF container_no IS NOT NULL THEN REGEXP_MATCH(container_no, ''^[A-Z]{4}[0-9]{7}$'')",
