          "expected_behavior": "Container number matches ISO 6346 pattern.",
          "failure_example": "''CONT123'' — incorrect format.",
          "pass_example": "''MAEU1234567''",
          "remediation": "Add ISO 6346 regex validation. Implement check digit verification algorithm."
        }
      ]
