## 5. 🔗 Cross-Field Rule Insights

### 5.1 Most Complex Field Interdependencies

| Rule | Fields Involved | Risk if Violated |
|---|---|---|
| Net Weight ≤ Gross Weight | net_weight_kg + gross_weight_kg | 🔴 Customs duty miscalculation |
| B/L required when SEA | transport_mode + bill_of_lading_no | 🔴 Cargo release blocked |
| AWB required when AIR | transport_mode + awb_no | 🔴 Customs clearance failure |
| Sea-only Incoterms for AIR | transport_mode + incoterm_code | 🔴 ICC compliance violation |
| Port of Loading matches Origin | port_of_loading + origin_country_code | 🟠 Customs declaration mismatch |
| Port of Discharge matches Destination | port_of_discharge + destination_country_code | 🟠 Routing error |
| CIF/CIP requires insurance_amount | incoterm_code + insurance_amount | 🟠 Customs valuation error |
| Insurance amount requires currency | insurance_amount + freight_currency | 🟠 Financial reporting error |
| Freight amount requires currency | freight_amount + freight_currency | 🔴 ZATCA valuation incomplete |
| created_at ≤ updated_at | created_at + updated_at | 🟡 Audit trail corruption |
| Shipment date not future for completed | shipment_date + shipment_status | 🔴 Regulatory filing error |
| Container no required for FCL | container_no + container_type + transport_mode | 🟠 Port manifest mismatch |

### 5.2 Field Dependency Map

```
transport_mode
    ├──► bill_of_lading_no     (required if SEA)
    ├──► awb_no                (required if AIR)
    ├──► vessel_flight_no      (required if SEA or AIR)
    ├──► container_no          (required if SEA + FCL)
    ├──► container_type        (required if SEA)
    ├──► incoterm_code         (sea-only codes invalid for AIR)
    ├──► port_of_loading       (required if SEA or AIR)
    └──► port_of_discharge     (required if SEA or AIR)

incoterm_code
    ├──► insurance_amount      (required if CIF or CIP)
    └──► freight_amount        (affects customs valuation basis)

container_no
    └──► seal_no               (required if container present)

freight_amount
    └──► freight_currency      (required if amount populated)

insurance_amount
    └──► freight_currency      (shares currency field)

gross_weight_kg
    └──► net_weight_kg         (net must not exceed gross)

shipment_status
    ├──► shipment_date         (must be past if COMPLETED/DELIVERED)
    ├──► carrier_name          (mandatory if BOOKED or beyond)
    └──► shipment_ref_no       (mandatory if not DRAFT)

origin_country_code
    └──► port_of_loading       (LOCODE prefix must match)

destination_country_code
    └──► port_of_discharge     (LOCODE prefix must match for IMPORT)

created_at
    └──► updated_at            (updated_at must be ≥ created_at)
```

