## 9. ⚠️ Business Logic Warning Insights

### 9.1 Top 10 Business Logic Warnings Identified

| # | Warning | Field(s) | Severity | Recommendation |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | No cancellation_reason field exists in the schema | shipment_status | 🔴 Critical | Add cancellation_reason field or create shipment_events table |
| 2 | No exchange_rate_to_sar field for foreign currency freight | freight_currency, freight_amount | 🔴 Critical | Add exchange_rate_to_sar field linked to SAMA daily rates |
| 3 | No export_license_no field for controlled destinations | destination_country_code | 🟠 High | Add export_license_no field for controlled country shipments |
| 4 | bill_of_lading_no and awb_no not mutually exclusive enforced | bill_of_lading_no, awb_no | 🟠 High | Add constraint: only one document type per transport mode |
| 5 | No updated_by field for audit trail completeness | updated_at | 🟠 High | Add updated_by field alongside updated_at |
| 6 | final_destination is free text with no structured address model | final_destination | 🟡 Medium | Decompose into city, region, country sub-fields |
| 7 | carrier_name is free text with no reference table enforced | carrier_name | 🟡 Medium | Link to ref_carriers table; add SCAC/IATA code field |
| 8 | No volumetric weight field derived from volume_cbm | volume_cbm, gross_weight_kg | 🟡 Medium | Add volumetric_weight_kg computed field for freight billing |
| 9 | No total_customs_value_sar derived field | freight_amount, insurance_amount | 🟠 High | Add total_customs_value_sar as computed/stored field |
| 10 | shipment_status has no timestamp tracking per transition | shipment_status | 🟠 High | Add shipment_status_history table with timestamp per transition |

