          "rule_type": "Cross-Field",
          "rule_description": "Certain Incoterms are exclusive to sea/inland waterway transport (FAS, FOB, CFR, CIF). Using them with air, road, or rail transport modes is a compliance error per ICC 2020.",
          "rule_expression": "IF incoterm_code IN (''FAS'', ''FOB'', ''CFR'', ''CIF'') THEN transport_mode IN (''SEA'', ''INLAND_WATERWAY'') ELIF incoterm_code IN (''FCA'', ''CPT'', ''CIP'', ''DAP'', ''DPU'', ''DDP'', ''EXW'') THEN transport_mode IN (''AIR'', ''ROAD'', ''RAIL'', ''SEA'', ''MULTIMODAL'')",
